kage_contents:\n      bin:\n        - idt\n      files:\n        - if: unix\n          then:\n            - share/bash-completion/completions/idt\n            - share/fish/vendor_completions.d/idt.fish\n            - share/zsh/site-functions/_idt\n        - if: win\n          then:\n            - Library/share/bash-completion/completions/idt\n            - Library/share/fish/vendor_completions.d/idt.fish\n            - Library/share/zsh/site-functions/_idt\n      strict: true\n\nabout:\n  homepage: https://github.com/sh-cho/idt\n  summary: A fast, ergonomic CLI tool for working with various ID formats\n  license: MIT OR Apache-2.0\n  license_file:\n    - LICENSE-APACHE\n    - LICENSE-MIT\n    - THIRDPARTY.yml\n  documentation: https://sh-cho.github.io/idt\n  repository: https://github.com/sh-cho/idt\n\nextra:\n  recipe-maintainers:\n    - salim-b\n",
